257
00:19:45,001 --> 00:19:55,000
Sa enpòtan anpil.

258
00:19:55,001 --> 00:19:59,000
Derive toujou pi difisil pase sa.

259
00:19:59,001 --> 00:20:03,000
Ou pa ka chape anba difikilte sa a.

260
00:20:03,001 --> 00:20:05,000
